title: Trump Toilet Paper Created By Local Artist
text:
Trump Toilet Paper Created By Local Artist Democrats showed off paper at debate viewing party Tracy Lehr , KEYT - KCOY - KKFX Reporter, tracy@keyt.com POSTED: 11:56 PM PDT Oct 13, 2015 Donald Trump toilet paper has people rolling with laughter SANTA BARBARA, Calif. - 
People waiting in line to attend a Democratic viewing party in Santa Barbara found some levity in a roll of toilet paper with a likeness of Donald Trump on every square. Related Content 
Rick Closson said he bought the roll online from a local artist named Dan Levin. 
Levin gained international attention when he made John McCain toilet paper back in 2008. 
Closson shared his Trump toilet paper and had fellow democrats rolling with laughter.
